{"tid":332204,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好掛住自己既初戀/第一個暗戀既人","createTime":"2017-07-22T20:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T20:55:10.000Z","uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c8289de066335743eae8f5622863f38822f3a4","tid":332204,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T20:31:48.000Z","msg":"雖然我地好耐無見<br />\n我唔會唔記得暗戀你既感覺<br />\n雖然我地都大個左 諗野唔同左<br />\n我唔會唔記得當年仲係好小朋友既我地<br />\n成日鬥咀成日搞我個頭又成日蝦我串我<br />\n你係我以前一放小息放學第一時間見既人<br />\n你係第一個令我最動心既人<br />\n係你令我明白愛一個人係可以唔介意對方既年齡同性別（sheshe)<br />\n其實之後都拍過幾次拖 <br />\n唔知點解都係唔夠同你一齊既日子深刻<br />\n用左成兩年先放得低你 <br />\n相反之前既分手半年左右已經放低左<br />\n係咪陳奕迅首粵語殘片入面既一句⋯⋯<br />\n奇怪卻是每戀一次 震撼總逐漸變得越淺<br />\n令人動心只得那次"},{"pid":"840bdfb584ac864431c2c9256ac516b4a48ad90e","tid":332204,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T20:42:03.000Z","msg":"初戀真係最深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我連自己密碼都set哂同佢d重要日子<br />\n佢送俾我隻錶都keep著戴足6年"},{"pid":"f99e641f611b5a8fcc10584b9dcf822c406f78bb","tid":332204,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T20:44:31.000Z","msg":"人就唔掛<br />\n掛住段回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b11a7b87fee6d436a2f4c362a1e83575a86afb1","tid":332204,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T20:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人就唔掛<br />\n掛住段回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyes"},{"pid":"5a0e976dfe5400ff630d04f9b662b4ed95defadc","tid":332204,"uid":51329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T20:54:08.000Z","msg":"岩岩突然好掛住佢<br />\n竟然有人開post<br />\n<br />\n我知道我只係太寂寞，無人可戀，總要搵啲目標寄托情感。而我依家隨便一個人都能夠戀上⋯<br />\n<br />\n我知道我根本唔記得初戀係咩滋味。<br />\n我知道我唔係掛住初戀，係掛住全部既ex，只係自己身邊連目標都無，要催眠自己，填補內心。<br />\n<br />\n但我真係好掛住佢<br />\n當佢係外國放暑假返翻香港既時候，我經常去佢出現既地方，希望可以撞到佢，之後笑住同我講，你知唔知道我等左你好耐？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec12133e2b4b18685179d6e386f42cee8e3fe97","tid":332204,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T20:55:08.000Z","msg":"我依幾日都成日諗起佢 唔知叫唔叫做掛住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7692b51b7c9a167e2b75bf100ccde68b571c1c4e","tid":332204,"uid":37283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人就唔掛<br />\n掛住段回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440586aabd7dd57b117adc2ecd0ceacf1fc5e2dd","tid":332204,"uid":238391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T20:27:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a69dd656fa95bd1f464aebee678a0fee1fb061b","tid":332204,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"440586aabd7dd57b117adc2ecd0ceacf1fc5e2dd","tid":332204,"uid":238391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T20:27:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T20:55:10.000Z","msg":"做乜起我底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}